        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>David Dorn Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill increases criminal penalties for rioting and related offenses (e.g., inciting a riot).</p> <p>Specifically, the bill increases the maximum prison term from 5 to 10 years. Additionally, if a fine is imposed for an offense, the bill sets a minimum fine amount of $1,000.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
